description:
{{sbc|Innate:}} Every time '''Zac''' damages at least one enemy with an [[Champion ability|ability]], he sheds, depending on the ability, {{tt|a number of chunks|• Depending on the ability the amount of produced chunks can vary:&#013;
&nbsp;• Stretching Strikes: Maximum of 2 chunks, 1 chunk for each strike hit on a different target. The collision does not produce additional chunks.&#013;
&nbsp;• Unstable Matter: Maximum of 1 chunk, no matter how many enemies hit.&#013;
&nbsp;• Elastic Slingshot: Maximum of 5 chunks, 1 chunk for each enemy champion hit.&#013;
&nbsp;• Let's Bounce!: Maximum of 4 chunks, 1 chunk for each bounce that hits one or more enemy champion.}} of himself to a nearby location, landing towards {{tip|sight|visible}} nearby enemy champions and lasting for 6 seconds.

E.notes:
* {{sbc|[[Quick cast]]ing:}} ''Elastic Slingshot's'' channel begins when the key is pressed and held, launching '''Zac''' towards the cursor when released.
* ''Elastic Slingshot'' will not {{tip|airborne|knock up}} if the targeted location was directly on top of '''Zac''' (in which case he will not {{tip|dash}} at all).{{bug|2}}
** The {{tip|airborne|knock up}} will occasionally end early if the targeted location was slightly away from '''Zac'''.{{bug|2}}
* {{tip|Displacement immunity}} will also resist the application of the {{tip|stun}}.
* The following table refers for interactions while '''Zac''' is {{tip|channel|channeling}}:
{{ct|charge|move=Disabled for the first {{fd|0.9}} seconds, otherwise, interrupts.|attack=false|cast={{ai|Stretching Strikes|Zac}} and {{ai|Unstable Matter|Zac}} interrupt. {{ai|Let's Bounce!|Zac}} initiates the recast.|items=interrupts,true,,false|spells=true,false,false,interrupts,recasts|interrupts = silence, death, root, ground}}
